Package com.netflix.spectator.ipc

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IpcLogEntry
    Builder used to fill in and submit a log entry associated with an IPC request.
    IpcLogger
    Logger for recording IPC metrics and providing a basic access log.
    NetflixHeaders
    Helper for extracting Netflix header values from the environment variables available on the base ami.
    ServerGroup
    Helper for parsing Netflix server group names that follow the Frigga conventions.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IpcAttempt
    Dimension indicating the retry attempt.
    IpcAttemptFinal
    Dimension indicating if it is the final attempt for a given request.
    IpcErrorGroup
    Dimension indicating a high level cause for the request failure.
    IpcMetric
    IPC metric names and associated metadata.
    IpcProtocol
    Dimension indicating the protocol.
    IpcResult
    Dimension indicating the overall result of the request.
    IpcTagKey
    Standard dimensions used for IPC metrics.
    NetflixHeader
    Headers in use at Netflix to relay information between the client and the server.
